<h1 class="h4">WebGL Game of Life</h1>

<p class="body2 textSecondary">
  An implementation of Conway's Game of Life using WebGL shaders.
  The board state is stored in two textures. On each step, a fragment shader will calulate
  the next state of the board from one texture and save it to the other.
</p>

<p class="primary caption">
  INSTRUCTIONS
</p>
<ul>
  <li>Toggle - play/pause the Game of Life.</li>
  <li>Step - progress one step.</li>
</ul>

<div class="app">
  <div>
    <button id="toggle">Toggle</button>
    <button id="step">Step</button>
  </div>
  <div>
    <canvas width="256" height="128" id="gol" class="pixelated"></canvas>
  </div>
</div>
